Output examples/svgs/everyday/neofetch.svg
Set Theme github-dark

Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Template macos
Set FontSize 22
Set FontSize 16
Set Scroll false
Set LineHeight 1
Set PromptPrefix "\x1b[32m> \x1b[0m"

Type "neofetch"

Sleep 500ms

Enter

Sleep 2s

Type "Welcome to DVD!"

Sleep 1s

Space

Type "A tool for generating terminal SVGs from code. Gggg"
Sleep 200ms
Shift+Left 5

Sleep 1s